# Version
$ ruby -v
ruby 2.0.0p353 (2013-11-22 revision 43784) [x86_64-linux]

# Run the MVC example
$ ./mvcpatterndemo.rb

##############################################################################
The intention is to give a very simple MVC example from first principles
(without using a web framework or other framework library).

This ruby program gives a small enhancement to MVC example in folder
example_mvc. The change gives a more interesting controller with a
simple event-loop.

